import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client'

import App from './App'

let counter = 1


const refresh = () => {
    ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root')).render(
      <App counter={counter} />
    )
  }
  setInterval(() => {
    refresh()
    counter += 1
  }, 1000)
  refresh()
  counter += 1
  refresh()
  counter += 1
  refresh()
